Alphonse Karr 2 Gallon (4'-6' Tall)

Visit
Small, tropical clumping or non-invasive bamboo that makes a great specimen plant but slow to produce a privacy screen. Bambusa multiplex 'Alphonse Karr' is a tropical clumping bamboo great for a small hedge or specimen plant. This species should only be planted in climate zone 8 and above.
* Check website for latest pricing and availability. Images may be subject to copyright. Learn More
